name: .UPOI File Extension
summary: Learn about .UPOI files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Contains points of interest (POIs) that can be saved along with a GPS navigation map; used by iGO 2008 for marking and saving locations within a map.

content: UPOI files may be imported into various navigation programs and can be converted to other formats using the online POI Editor.
